                    VALUE
FREQUENCY           600
PROBABILITY         10
REPLAYDELAY         150
SPECIALPROBABILITY  25

# knobs for tuning how often NPCs start their banter dialogs
# FREQUENCY is the base check period in ticks, checked against current game time
# PROBABILITY further limits the occurrence when FREQUENCY matches
# SPECIALPROBABILITY is limiting the same NPC bantering in a row
# REPLAYDELAY is unused
